{"id": 1267, "genre": 1000, "title": "如何选择餐厅让你更像一个中产阶级？", "description": "人是铁，范儿是钢，一天不装憋得慌。对于中产阶级这个可爱的群体，我们充满了爱意。好奇心研究所会不定期推出紧跟时代节奏的“中产阶级装腔指南”，和大家一起分享研究生活的心得。（题图来自：behance）", "record_count": 11739, "comment_count": 45, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161009230952DwZeJVEXU6Laj5l1.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-10-30T17:00:37Z", "questions": [{"id": 1200, "title": "如何选择餐厅让你更像一个中产阶级？", "content": "如何选择餐厅让你更像一个中产阶级？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 122194, "content": "不盲目迷信大众点评", "image": "img/option/option/20161009181742WFZP2TtfhKwxoJGa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 122195, "content": "讲究有机，从农场到餐桌", "image": "img/option/option/20161009181809O30eam59hNlGzQ17.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 122198, "content": "有团购的一般不去", "image": "img/option/option/20161009182203Dq8ieoCJuPNlRSct.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 122199, "content": "会冲着某个主厨去吃饭", "image": "img/option/option/20161009183203BX47RuG26OYexdVE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 122200, "content": "根据米其林指南进行“摘星式觅食”", "image": "img/option/option/20161009183216k1ueOc3vqlLJnU6p.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 122201, "content": "去食材原产地的餐厅去吃", "image": "img/option/option/201610091832379F7ERVQZsIuDr0lM.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 122203, "content": "愿意尝试创新口味餐厅", "image": "img/option/option/20161009181839nrTCol2MDRKstAVb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}